data.description: Gorgeous views of Devils Lake!!  Paradise awaits!  This well-built home has vaulted ceilings with an open floor plan.  Enjoy views of the lake, mountains, and wildlife from your large deck or the main living areas of the home.  Situated on Devils Lake in what locals call "The Banana Belt" due to its protection from the coastal winds. Spacious yard and private access to your dock.
